$(4)$ Calculate: $(\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}+1}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{5}+\sqrt{3}}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{7}+\sqrt{5}}+\ldots +\frac{1}{\sqrt{2023}+\sqrt{2021}})\times (\sqrt{2023}+1)$.

